    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/974d200f00ab12b2d450cfda18ff53d1.poster.avif?t=1753467192\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/974d200f00ab12b2d450cfda18ff53d1.webm?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/974d200f00ab12b2d450cfda18ff53d1.mp4?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/c3206a851e8a653a85a84263fa466e36.poster.avif?t=1753467192\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/c3206a851e8a653a85a84263fa466e36.webm?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/c3206a851e8a653a85a84263fa466e36.mp4?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dark Age Legends</strong> 是一款回合制战斗机制的游戏，在战斗中以及整个旅程中，策略性的决策都至关重要。在旅途中，你需要选择最正义的道路，并招募最合适的冠军加入你的队伍。解锁这些冠军的新技能，将他们塑造为真正的传奇。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建你的队伍！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你遇到的敌人可能是成群结队，也可能是庞大的怪物。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自旅行非常危险！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/9ecda9ad6d1a7f78ca55c6b7eddbba69.poster.avif?t=1753467192\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/9ecda9ad6d1a7f78ca55c6b7eddbba69.webm?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/9ecda9ad6d1a7f78ca55c6b7eddbba69.mp4?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >谨慎做出选择！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正确的队伍、合适的装备、明智的抉择和精妙的策略，都是通往胜利道路的关键。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色都有独特的技能和玩法风格，在合适的位置和队伍中，他们可以发挥强大的力量。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你在旅途中打败敌人获得的材料制作特殊装备，全副武装，准备挑战强大的首领。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗策略必须在旅程之初就决定远在真正战斗开始之前……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/eb2de7c4dba9844213d944999a46e9bf.poster.avif?t=1753467192\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/eb2de7c4dba9844213d944999a46e9bf.webm?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350630/extras/eb2de7c4dba9844213d944999a46e9bf.mp4?t=1753467192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
